---checkup---

Hello my bby! I just want to say thank you for helping me sa checkups ko kahit na it eats a lot of time! I love you so much!

One thing na narealize ko all throughout this ordeal is that, gusto ko pa talaga mabuhay ng matagal HAHAHAHA. Tatanda pa tayo hanggang 80 kaya nung nag papacheckup ako and nag papa test ganun, talagang pinag dadasal ko na maganda lahat ng results kase jusko po gusto ko pa makasama bbycakes ko ng super tagal huhu.

Kaya bby!! Let's be healthy okay? I love you so much and I want to spend the rest of ny long long life with you! Kaya alagaan naten sarili naten ha? MWAA!!

---CONGRATSSS!---

Congratulations for finally getting the job that you want my princess!! I'm so so happy for you! I was there with you all throughout kaya alam na alam ko gaano mo kagusto yan! And finally seeing you achieve it makes me so so happy!

I'm so excited for you! And I'm also really really happy that you get another big step for your carreer! Gagaling at gagaling ka diyan! And whenever things get stressful, I'm always here for you to rely on okay? I LOVE YOU!!!
